videos.headline: Troy's B.J. Smith runs 12 yards for TD
videos.description: B.J. Smith bursts 12 yards for the touchdown, putting Troy up on Louisiana 17-3.

videos.headline: Louisiana's Ragas slips in for TD
videos.description: Trey Ragas takes the handoff and slips through the Troy defense for the Louisiana touchdown.

videos.headline: Ragas smashes his way to second TD
videos.description: Trey Ragas powers through a Troy defender to score his second touchdown of the day for Louisiana.

videos.headline: Louisiana's Nunez throws INT straight to Troy defense
videos.description: Andre Nunez's pass is thrown directly to Troy's Kyler Knudsen, who comes up with the interception.
